<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#950000">"الجرح والتعديل"</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٤/ ١٨١)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
